{"tid":1193144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6.9遊行 迫人表態真係咁重要咩？...","createTime":"2019-06-08T18:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T19:14:47.000Z","uid":207000,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf746bcdf31e81663feedf74581f3eeb67f670a4","tid":1193144,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港有言論自由</span></span><br />\n我地都捍衛緊呢份自由<br />\n而我唔明白嘅係<br />\n點解要迫人表態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係咁重要咩 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">迫個啞嘅表態真係咁重要咩<br />\n我覺得唔重要<br />\n完全係哂時間...</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日見到大家係到屌黎屌去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過留返啲精力 <br />\n臨訓睇多幾次個啲教人聽日點保護好自己嘅post仲好<br />\n身為香港人 發出自己嘅聲音係好重要<br />\n但<span style=\"color: gold;\">保護好自己都好重要</span></span><br />\n另外 企係同一個立場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">見到youtuber 海外嘅港人 upload 片撐反送中<br />\n係一件<span style=\"color: red;\">振奮 提升凝聚力</span>嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇出聲個啲咪由佢囉</span></span><br />\n得返咁少時間 出聲嘅讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為多一份影響力係到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇出聲嘅 唔洗下下屌</span></span><br />\n留返精力聽日一齊加油<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">留返精力去鼓勵更多同一立場嘅人出黎仲好啦..</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係連登做開花生友 但距離遊行剩返唔夠一日<br />\n都仲見到好多<span style=\"color: red;\">無謂嘅嘈交</span><br />\n真係睇見都攰 所以第一次咁樣開po留低自己嘅想法</span><br />\n好撚多固執撚 好撚多膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">由佢地啦屌 講多無謂。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我都係固執撚 不過我覺得我企啱立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日見 加油 同埋見到香港人係咁短時間<br />\n做咗咁多傳單 咁多宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（宣傳仲要同班收錢嘅嘈）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好自豪 你地話我岸久都好<br />\n我都係好自豪咁講<br />\n我愛香港人 呢個地方幾辛苦都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有你地真係好開心 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預咗比人搵位屌</span> 我只不過想分享我嘅意見<br />\n屌得舒服嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">隨便</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同同一立場嘅香港人講聲 聽日見<br />\n黎唔到嘅 都希望為遊行嘅人加油<br />\n多一個唔多 少一個唔少？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實邊理得咁多😂😂<br />\n我都只係做我認為啱嘅事 </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n我係一個土生土長嘅香港人🔥<br />\n點講都好 都唔想移民嘅香港人<br />\n同你地立場衝突都好 <br />\n想屌就屌 <span style=\"color: red;\">你有你道理 <br />\n我有我理由。</span>"},{"pid":"a3762db2ecaef3cccc4057d243180379f838bf57","tid":1193144,"uid":71509,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"聽日見<br />\n<br />\n不過有條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n踩住兄弟上位<br />\n<br />\n一開波由JTV 睇起<br />\n<br />\n又反共⋯ 又平反六四<br />\n<br />\n多人睇左， 上左位<br />\n<br />\n就咩都唔表態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信若果條撚樣一開始只係打機<br />\n<br />\n從來冇講過任何政治野<br />\n<br />\n而家唔會俾人迫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要⋯ 聽日見啊咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f39aa73ea9b0828a139c69a23d1306f5b6e87c4","tid":1193144,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:43:16.000Z","msg":"同埋我想問點放gif圖上黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想放 這是我的職責 個張<br />\n原來我垃圾 未開過po唔識放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c9a7a1a816c87b692615abb4f402b8afcf2b46","tid":1193144,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f39aa73ea9b0828a139c69a23d1306f5b6e87c4","tid":1193144,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:43:16.000Z","msg":"同埋我想問點放gif圖上黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想放 這是我的職責 個張<br />\n原來我垃圾 未開過po唔識放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"原諒* 不過原來都啱嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0e0ae28ae1e63d216f66c10722a9f0be7ea879","tid":1193144,"uid":207000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3762db2ecaef3cccc4057d243180379f838bf57","tid":1193144,"uid":71509,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"聽日見<br />\n<br />\n不過有條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n踩住兄弟上位<br />\n<br />\n一開波由JTV 睇起<br />\n<br />\n又反共⋯ 又平反六四<br />\n<br />\n多人睇左， 上左位<br />\n<br />\n就咩都唔表態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信若果條撚樣一開始只係打機<br />\n<br />\n從來冇講過任何政治野<br />\n<br />\n而家唔會俾人迫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要⋯ 聽日見啊咁多位<img src=\"/a